characteristic.__text: Any Combat Phase
Pick up to 3 friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh units to be the targets.

The targets have the **^^Euphoric^^** keyword for the rest of the battle round.
In addition, for each friendly unit you pick, give your opponent 1 temptation dice. Your opponent can use 1 temptation dice to replace 1 wound roll, 1 save roll, 1 ward roll or 1 run roll for a unit in their army with a 6, or they can use 2 temptation dice to replace 2 of the dice in a charge roll for a unit in their army with two 6s.
Each time your opponent uses a temptation dice, they must roll it. On a 1-2, inflict D3 mortal damage on the unit for which the roll was replaced immediately after the ability used by that unit has been resolved. At the end of the battle round, any temptation dice that have not been used are lost.

While a friendly unit has the **^^Euphoric^^** keyword:
• That unit’s weapons have **Crit (2 Hits)**.
• That unit can use a **^^Run^^** ability and still use **^^Shoot^^** and/or **^^Charge^^** abilities later in the turn.
Once Per Battle, Any Combat Phase
Pick a non-**^^Hero Hedonites of Slaanesh^^** unit wholly within 12" of this unit to be the target.
Add 1 to the Attacks characteristic of the target’s melee weapons for the rest of the turn.
Once Per Battle, Any Combat Phase
If any damage points were allocated to this unit this turn, **Heal (3)** this unit.
Once Per Battle, Any Combat Phase
For the rest of the turn, subtract 1 from the Attacks characteristic of melee weapons used by enemy units while they are in combat with this unit.
Add 1 to hit rolls for friendly **^^Sybarite Infantry^^** units while they are damaged or if they had any models slain in the same turn.

Friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Cavalry^^** units can use a **^^Retreat^^** ability and still use **^^Charge^^** abilities later in the turn. In addition, no mortal damage is inflicted on **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Cavalry^^** units by **^^Retreat^^** abilities.
Each time a friendly non-**^^Hero Hedonites of Slaanesh Daemon^^** uses the ‘Rally’ command, you can make 3 additional rally rolls of D6.
Add 3 to the control scores of friendly non-**^^Hero Hedonites of Slaanesh^^** units while they are within the combat ranges of any friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Heroes^^**.
Add 1 to hit rolls and wound rolls for this unit’s attacks while it is more than 6" from all other friendly units.
If an enemy **^^Hero^^** is destroyed by this unit, this unit has the **^^Euphoric^^** keyword for the rest of the battle.
If this unit charged this turn and the unmodified charge roll was 8+, this unit has Strike-first for the rest of the turn.
Your Hero Phase
If there is not a friendly **Mesmerising Mirror** on the battlefield, pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
Set up a **Mesmerising Mirror** wholly within 12" of the caster and visible to them.
Your Hero Phase
If there is not a friendly **Wheels of Excruciation** endless spell on the battlefield, pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
Set up a **Wheels of Excruciation** endless spell wholly within 12" of the caster, visible to them and more than 9" from all enemy units.
Your Hero Phase
If there is not a friendly **Dreadful Visage** on the battlefield, pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
If there is not a friendly **Dreadful Visage** on the battlefield, pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible friendly **^^Euphoric^^** unit to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
The target’s melee weapons have **Crit (Mortal)** instead of **Crit (2 Hits)** for the rest of the battle round.
**^^Spell^^**, **^^Unlimited^^**
Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible enemy unit within 18" of them to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.
Add 1 to wound rolls for attacks that target that enemy unit until the start of your next turn.
Your Hero Phase
Pick a friendly **^^Hedonites of Slaanesh Wizard^^** to cast this spell, pick a visible enemy unit within 12" of them to be the target, then make a casting roll of 2D6.

Until the start of your next turn, each time the target is picked to use a **^^Fight^^** ability, before reactions are used, you can pick a friendly unit in combat with the target. That friendly unit can move 2D3". It can pass through the combat ranges of enemy units and can end that move in combat.
